{"tid":1418853,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[割蓆］你班所謂嘅勇武唔代表我哋和理非","createTime":"2019-08-05T21:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T21:33:13.000Z","uid":135336,"like":11,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"08306cbb43480d1a6777bc59c558a9405df95cfb","tid":1418853,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:03:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母，前線攞自己嘅青春、自己條命，去賭香港嘅未來  </span></span>，你班企到後一後，索過兩下催淚彈，就post上ig攞光環嘅撚樣，做過啲咩呀？ 場仗都未撚打完，就清算前線，搞分化，有光環你就衝出嚟拎，見勢色唔對路，就急急腳割蓆<br />\n<br />\n講好咗就算玩核彈都唔割蓆㗎嘛，宜家又將前線用完即棄<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">你哋係咪想以後都無人肯做前線呀？場仗仲想唔想贏㗎？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2bb3247f1ba6b245f97c9a81a514d91b7aa077","tid":1418853,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:04:55.000Z","msg":"要求暫停P牌發表主題、正負評及回覆功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418574\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418574</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f918dce24c248033f16d10195aa446055c06dd04","tid":1418853,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:11:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 俾撚完負皮就走"},{"pid":"78289ddf49a7b11017c966e009d8402863a9935f","tid":1418853,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:12:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5da6ca314b19c0dba9da66daa03ace04f7c7a53","tid":1418853,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b12bc2735fd9588fefb455d81c0c69b1cee2fb5","tid":1418853,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:12:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d63310f45b4ca3df6c05d28693d02d5e0c05fea4","tid":1418853,"uid":135336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T21:12:3